# API base URL (no trailing slash). Set via EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL.
#
# - Web / browser on same machine: default http://localhost:5000/api is fine.
# - iOS device or simulator / Android device: use your laptop's LAN IP so the
#   device can reach the backend, e.g.:
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.100:5000/api
#
# Find your IP: Windows: ipconfig  |  Mac/Linux: ifconfig or ip addr
# Then restart Expo (npm start) after setting the variable.
